dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Creston & Shedd Canyon quadrangles, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base maps from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle CRESTON, CA 1948, DMA 1855 II SE -- V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980; SHEDD CANYON, CA 1961 REVISED 1993."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
